h1b$WAGE_RATE_FROM <- as.numeric(h1b$LCA_CASE_WAGE_RATE_FROM)
h1b$EMPLOYER_POSTAL_CODE <- as.numeric(h1b$LCA_CASE_EMPLOYER_POSTAL_CODE)
